<%- include('header'); -%>


    <%- include('nav'); -%>


        <div class="mx-auto px-4 py-4 container-fluid">
            <h3 id="login-form"><%= title %></h3>
            <p>When a user logs in via this form, a post request is created which takes the user's email address and compares it with those of previously registered users. If there is an existing user whose email matches the one submitted, the post request will use the bcrypt.hash() and bcrypt.compare() methods to create a hashed version of the entered password and compare it against the one saved in the user database for the relevant user. If it is a match, the user will be alerted to the successful login and redirected to the homepage, where they will now have access to additional navigation items, including User Details and Logout.</p>
            <div class="mx-2 px-2 mb-4 pb-4">
                    <div class="card-body my-auto">
                        <form action="/login" method="post">
                            <div class="row my-2">
                                <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                                    <label for="email" class="my-1">Email</label>
                                    <input type="email" name="email" id="email" class="form-control">
                                    
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                                    <label for="password" class="my-1">Password</label>
                                    <input type="password" name="password" id="password" class="form-control">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        
                            <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-block m-auto p-auto">
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Log In</button>
                            </div>
                            
                        </form>
                    <div class="card-footer my-auto">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center links">
                            Don't have an account? <a href="/register-page">Register</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                            <a href="#">Forgot your password?</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                
         
            </div>

        </div>



        
    
    <%- include('footer'); -%>

